precis:
SCHEDULE NO. 250 to the MOTOR VEHICLE SAFETY REGULATIONS - which corrects
certain inconsistencies in the wording of the safety standards in section
115 (Vehicle Identification Number), as well as a number of other
discrepancies between the English and French versions pertaining to seat
belt assemblies and other restraint systems.
